<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1066855-how-would-this-book-have-been-different-if">How would this book have been different if it had been told from a man&#39;s POV?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1066855'><a id="like_count_community_question_1066855" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/1066855?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">1 like</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F122212.Waiting_to_Exhale">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
